f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3158c15beee99d66c3c1c0d6c863ec7d7c12cc37","tid":1842431,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:36:15.000Z","msg":"入去自推十連！要十分鐘內上熱門！<br />\n<br />\n請不要再說：「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5a48123c37312c3f79b391f7a77c75debe5792ff","tid":1842431,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36fae709858de42d4f19ab068180826844f22806","tid":1842431,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"呢個病搞到今時今日咁，都係因為共產黨班撚樣同一班冇腦既中國人，點解你地要承受佢地製造出嚟既災難<br />\n兩個禮拜前，中國人同政府仲笑鳩我地過份恐慌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解我地要為咗大陸班仆街，攞條命嚟博</span></span><br />\n我同你講：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔值得呀</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人完全支持你罷工！<br />\n因為你都係一個人嚟噶！<br />\n你都有權利生存噶！！！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最主要係，嗰啲唔理自己會唔會傳染俾人既大陸人，唔值得俾你救呀！佢地連人地條命都唔重視既人，憑乜嘢要我地尊重佢？</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總之</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今次疫症我唔俾有任何一個醫護手足犧牲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">由宜家開始<br />\n請立即發起醫護界罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直到香港政府<br />\n1.遣返所有內地受感染病人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.封鎖所有內地關口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.要求內地如實向國際公佈疫情最新狀況，不得隱瞞或壓低疫情實況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">至於全部香港人，我都希望你地做多步，全面提升社區防疫意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n講真由上而下既防疫措施其實唔可以真正救到香港，屌你老母政府係靠得住唔洗宜家咁啦，唯有由市民自身做起，再推己及人，先係最有效防疫<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1.見義勇為 勇敢發聲</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭車見到有仆街又咳又唔戴口罩，麻煩開聲屌，我相信香港人宜家出街聽到有咳嗽聲都會驚，佢唔配合就請佢即刻落車<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2.家庭教育</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家中廢佬如果唔肯戴口罩，麻煩屌撚到佢開花，開電視播住肺炎新聞，手機播住啲大陸疫情影片，唔肯戴麻煩咪撚俾佢出門口害人，恩威並施<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3.多啲關心身邊既人</span></span><br />\n問下啲朋友 買唔買到口罩，試下一齊訂外國口罩，或者俾啲人，共渡時艱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">4.囤積糧食</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預防疫症喺香港進一步擴散，請隨時做好要與世隔絕既準備，買啲啲米呀罐頭糧食<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5.積極學習防疫知識</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家平時見到啲警示文、教學post，麻煩唔好唔理，唔該細心閱讀、了解多啲，再同身邊既人講返<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.全民代購</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出國麻煩代購一堆醫護用品，好過手信十倍，口罩、N95唔洗講，宜家消毒藥水都有缺貨情況<br />\n<br />\nShare呢篇文出去，俾更加多人知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府防疫無能<br />\n醫護罷工自保</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:36:29.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"722bfd4e519a66c4a3a796cb9ca1a324f7124818","tid":1842431,"uid":345458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3006dbb53586a29d6525aff57f92274ff088b70a","tid":1842431,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:32:23.000Z","msg":"對唔住啱啱睇到個Post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我已經準備好<br />\n同醫護界一齊罷工<br />\n全民三罷！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n請不要再說：「我支持醫護罷工。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842379\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842379</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"我都睇到"},{"pid":"96612d3786d964057dfbaeb0d246d1d8550b7aa0","tid":1842431,"uid":51068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/977rMtW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F977rMtW.jpg&h=752334f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3z7bXAD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3z7bXAD.jpg&h=a4562288&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8cc86b040826a516dee636aba0b12cf0aa351a2c","tid":1842431,"uid":64126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T16:41:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">罷工唔止係醫護人員嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n係全香港700萬市民嘅責任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全港三罷 刻不容緩</span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oisbVO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoisbVO4.jpg&h=e95b4412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔罷 下一個中招嘅好可能係你</div>"},{"pid":"2cd53e23e768f7dad5ac48cfa8bf347152545cbb","tid":1842431,"uid":68982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:25:51.000Z","msg":"點解淨係叫醫護罷工？明明封關關乎全香港人生命保障。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1841737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1841737</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9dcccccacbfa3b9bc2d8e89002a36e2df82c33e3","tid":1842431,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:47:26.000Z","msg":"醫護唔罷工，就係因為歷史罪人！你地想死，想做左膠，香港人唔想！"},{"pid":"5092da51e353be2a55e0a353f92f6fa431c89913","tid":1842431,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T18:47:55.000Z","msg":"*就係"}]}